Elgg Database Cleaner

It has a validate and clean mode. It can fix the following problems:

1. user without a username
2. entity with owner_guid set to 0 (object or group)
3. entity with a deleted owner
4. entity that is missing an entry in its <type> table

It will also try to fix out of memory errors caused by corruption of enabled
plugins. You must hit the URL: http//yoursite.com/mod/dbvalidate/repair.php

Currently, it assumes its directory is set to dbvalidate.

